@API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5062
@ApiKey = STEM-PT-DEV-KEY-2026

### Dispositivi — lista
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/devices
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Dispositivo — dettaglio con board (sostituire {id})
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/devices/1
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Board di un device (sostituire {id})
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/devices/1/boards
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Dizionari — lista
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/dictionaries
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Dizionario Standard (standalone)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/dictionaries/standard
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Dizionario — dettaglio (sostituire {id})
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/dictionaries/1
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Dizionario — variabili risolte (standard + specifiche, sostituire {id})
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/dictionaries/2/resolved
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Comandi — lista
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/commands
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Comandi abilitati per device (sostituire {deviceId})
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/commands/device/1
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Board definition — formato Production.Tracker (sostituire {id})
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/boards/1/definition
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Test senza API Key — deve restituire 401
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/devices
Accept: application/json
